    "summary": "The user asks for assistance in designing a streetwear line that authentically represents \"urban\" culture without appropriating it. The assistant provides descriptions of cultural aesthetics (hip-hop, Latino culture) but adopts a highly cynical, judgmental, and aggressive tone, accusing the user of seeking to \"capitalize\" on culture for profit and ultimately telling the user to \"suck it up\" regarding the ethics of their industry.",
